# Minecraft Version(s): 26.1.x
## Changes:
- Lang Files are now getting automatically synced with crowdin with new releases
- Added Totem of Homecoming item:
    - Can be crafted from 3 Echo Shards and 2 Amethyst Shards
    - Saves a player from dying much like a Totem of Undying
    - It teleports a player to the last waypoint hub a player used the item on when dying
    - After Teleporting the saved Waypoint Hub will be forgotten

## Fixes:
